---
title: Apricot-Mumbai Chicken & Curry Potatoes with Cucumber & Carrot Ribbon Salad
description: Get ready for a flavour-packed adventure! Succulent, Mumbai-spiced chicken gets a sweet coating of apricot sauce, paired with creamy, fluffy smashed potatoes infused with curry powder. Add a refreshing cucumber and carrot ribbon salad for crunch and brightness.

